Disclaimer
----------
SkillForge is an educational hackathon project, provided as is and without
warranty of any kind. It is not a hiring, promotion, or certification tool. The
role competency profiles and the seed corpus are illustrative and cover only a
sample of network, cloud, and security roles. Readiness scores are intended as a
learning aid, not as a qualification of record.

Third-party services
---------------------
When configured, SkillForge calls Microsoft Foundry (the Phi-4-mini-instruct
model endpoint) and Foundry IQ (Azure AI Search). Use of those services is
subject to their own terms. Credentials are read from a local .env file, which
is gitignored and must never be committed.
